{"tid":131242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文匯報轟曾俊華過去網誌有偷步競選之嫌","createTime":"2017-02-23T02:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T03:54:48.000Z","uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7bfd54ce8b54a05cae5d23131fe39d332d435bd4","tid":131242,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:41:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%87%E5%8C%AF-%E6%96%B0%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E%E8%BD%9F%E6%9B%BE%E4%BF%8A%E8%8F%AF-%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E7%B6%B2%E8%AA%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%81%B7%E6%AD%A5%E7%AB%B6%E9%81%B8%E4%B9%8B%E5%AB%8C-%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E8%99%95%E6%87%89%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E8%BF%BD%E7%A9%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%25AF-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25A7%2580%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25BD%259F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E4%25BF%258A%25E8%258F%25AF-%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258E%25BB%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E8%25AA%258C%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2581%25B7%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%25AB%258C-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E7%25A9%25B6%2F&d=QRr32DkYW87Xu5pQ%2FNKRK49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=8445c577\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%25AF-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25A7%2580%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25BD%259F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E4%25BF%258A%25E8%258F%25AF-%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258E%25BB%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E8%25AA%258C%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2581%25B7%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%25AB%258C-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E7%25A9%25B6%2F&h=387066de\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%87%E5%8C%AF-%E6%96%B0%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E%E8%BD%9F%E6%9B%BE%E4%BF%8A%E8%8F%AF-%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB%E7%B6%B2%E8%AA%8C%E6%9C%89%E5%81%B7%E6%AD%A5%E7%AB%B6%E9%81%B8%E4%B9%8B%E5%AB%8C-%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E8%99%95%E6%87%89%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E8%BF%BD%E7%A9%B6/</a><br />\n<br />\n垃場節錄:<br />\n<br />\n1. 曾俊華出任財政司司長剛剛20天開始寫網誌，直至辭職前一天的2016年12月11日時仍在發表，累計近430篇。網誌內容五花八門，包括：音樂、文學、電影、戲劇、運動、功夫等，更多的內容是飲飲食食，數量堪比財政事務主題，儼然成為一名「網上特首」。財爺網誌美其名曰讓大眾更加了解政策理念，事實上賦予了更多的政治抱負，通過網誌張揚個性、培養粉絲，潛心為競選特首作準備。<br />\n<br />\n2. 在告別網誌中，曾俊華發出了感慨，「只要有你們繼續與我同行，又何懼前路新挑戰？」這還不是為參選特首發出動員令，不是呼籲粉絲繼續支持他的競選工程。<br />\n<br />\n3. 想起了傳媒界的一則段子：採訪3名財金官員，曾俊華的回答經常以問句結束，反問傳媒記者；如果陳家強在場，曾俊華就把問題推給他，陳家強也善於「答非所問」；陳德霖可能是最認真回答的一個。最令人詬病的是，曾俊華任內連年估錯數，累計估少近5,000億港元盈餘；他任內7份預算案，6次預測會錄得赤字，但最終全部錄得盈餘。<br />\n<br />\n4. 曾俊華疏於日常政務，在網上勤力，形成鮮明對比，心水清的市民自有判斷。在任時心不在焉，或許目標早已鎖定行政長官的位置。"},{"pid":"11d90406bb15f1682b626a288851adcbdf8c85e5","tid":131242,"uid":59140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:55:09.000Z","msg":"嗰陣又唔係明刀明槍話要選特首<br />\n理得人啫"},{"pid":"c2df1eb3084564b40021ce266b7819ebd7c217e2","tid":131242,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:57:40.000Z","msg":"咁計法所有參選人+689+所有立法會議員睇怕都無一幸勉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6eef68fbefa75079d0c1b9fd0ee6cac73a6b26a","tid":131242,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:59:29.000Z","msg":"林病個網幾時注冊？"},{"pid":"75221c372c4e9b5818be01c6e399b49f7f677e0b","tid":131242,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:00:50.000Z","msg":"人地寫日記又話人偷步,江派人咁想搵證據dq薯片?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9ff527ecce9027b7d5bfbdc0e0730f59ec099b","tid":131242,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:01:50.000Z","msg":"冇其他嘢插啦？？"},{"pid":"d0e45e3dee66158e8b0e2b5b4bab9374153a367e","tid":131242,"uid":8106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:54:48.000Z","msg":"佢預計自己任期內會有六次錄得赤字<br />\n事後全部有盈餘 唔係好事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}